# Business Objectives

The primary objective of this project is to design and implement a digital platform
that enables Centip Trading International to successfully enter and operate in the
used car sales and service market.

The key business objectives are as follows:

## 1. Enable Digital Used Car Transactions
- Provide a platform for sellers to list used cars with complete details and photographs
- Allow buyers to search, compare, and purchase used cars based on model, make,
  price, and other criteria

## 2. Provide Transparent and Accurate Pricing
- Offer automated car price estimation using an algorithm
- Enable optional professional valuation by certified surveyors at an additional fee

## 3. Ensure Trust and Authenticity
- Verify vehicle documentation through an admin approval process
- Ensure authenticity and completeness of uploaded documents before listing approval

## 4. Simplify Ownership Transfer and Logistics
- Provide end-to-end support for ownership transfer through the logistics team
- Coordinate with Regional Transport Offices (RTOs) for legal formalities

## 5. Improve Operational Efficiency
- Reduce manual effort through automation of pricing and documentation workflows
- Standardize processes for valuation, approval, and ownership transfer

## 6. Enhance Customer Experience
- Create a reliable, user-friendly platform for buyers and sellers
- Reduce transaction time and increase customer confidence in used car purchases
